{
  "stem": "21013.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I might have been afraid of the reactions, because I felt that people who didn't actively hurt anybody and just looked on were just as guilty.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I felt that life was made easier for me being a victim.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I left England on Armistice Day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And leaving England during the war from Southampton harbor was not an easy matter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The woman that I lived with, this Muriel Blakey, took me by train to Southampton.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was one of these terribly foggy days that you only see in a Sherlock Holmes movie.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't see your hand in front of your face.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We got to Southampton and there was-- you just couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to get on a train and leave my friend and say goodbye to her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in the excitement, she was holding my raincoat and I didn't have a coat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I left that behind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got on the train, the boat train to the harbor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there I got off the train and got on to a tender somehow, in this thick fog.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And suddenly, out of the fog rose this great big hull of a gray ship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to go up on a rope ladder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was very difficult, the rope ladder was swaying and then the ocean below and it was really scary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we got up on the ship and there were guns all over and sandbags all over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got into my cabin and it was a cabin that was as big as my living room here.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was enormous and very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was a very luxurious-looking ship inside.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
